videos.headline: Rudolph's long pass to Ateman gets Oklahoma State in the red zone
videos.description: Mason Rudolph throws a strike to Marcell Ateman who races to the red zone on a 54-yard completion.

videos.headline: Rudolph, Oklahoma State score on first drive
videos.description: Mason Rudolph fakes the handoff and rushes to the outside for a 1-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Oklahoma State's Hill high-steps into the end zone
videos.description: Justice Hill finds a hole on the left side for a 12-yard touchdown run.

videos.headline: Rudolph gets second TD on 76-yard pass
videos.description: Mason Rudolph throws a beautiful deep ball to Dillon Stoner, who breaks a tackle for a 76-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Ateman puts Oklahoma State in Kansas territory with 31-yard catch
videos.description: Mason Rudolph zips a pass to Marcell Ateman in double coverage for a 31-yard catch at the Kansas 38-yard line.

videos.headline: Oklahoma State's Brown finds a little daylight for short TD run
videos.description: La'Darren Brown finds a small hole for a 1-yard touchdown run to put the Cowboys up 34-3 in the first half.

videos.headline: Kansas ends first half with great TD catch
videos.description: Peyton Bender goes for the big play and hooks up with Evan Fairs, who completes the catch and falls into the end zone for a 33-yard touchdown reception.

videos.headline: Oklahoma State gets its first takeaway
videos.description: Chad Whitener picks off Peyton Bender's pass and returns it 6 yards to set up short field for Oklahoma State.

videos.headline: Rudolph throws second TD pass on short field
videos.description: Mason Rudolph lobs a pass to James Washington in the end zone for a 30-yard touchdown pass.

videos.headline: Sims lunges for Kansas TD
videos.description: Steven Sims Jr. crosses the plane of the end zone for a 2-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Kansas' Sims slices through defenders for big return
videos.description: Steven Sims Jr. evades defenders and returns the kickoff for 35 yards.

videos.headline: Washington gets both feet in for 23-yard catch
videos.description: Mason Rudolph evades pass rushers and finds James Washington along the sidelines for a 23-yard catch.

videos.headline: Rudolph leaps into end zone for second rushing TD
videos.description: Mason Rudolph sells the handoff and takes it himself for a 1-yard touchdown run. It's Rudolph's fourth touchdown of the game.

videos.headline: Oklahoma State's Cornelius completes 56-yard pass on first throw of the day
videos.description: Backup quarterback Tyler Cornelius throws a 56-yard strike to Tyrell Alexander, which leads to a short Cowboys' touchdown.
